Kristanv mantat ki [[Jezu]]n koxtt sosle, to melo, taka nikipilo, ani to mornantlo punorjivont zalo, techer aplea patkanche bhogsonne mellche pasot visvas thevteleank sasnachem jivit diunche khatir.

Kristanvponnache tin vhoddle fantte zaun asat [[Katolik firgoz]], Orthodox firgoz, ani Protestant. Katolik ani Orthodox firgoz 11ve xekdeant vegle zalet, Protestant 16ve xekdean ostitvant ailem.

